</div>
<div>
<p>
<measure quantity="2" unit="months">
<num value="2">二</num>月</measure>
<num value="5">戊辰</num>
<pc>，</pc>鼻骨德奏軍籍<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="3" unit="months">
