</div>
<div>
<p>
<measure quantity="5" unit="months">
<num value="5">五</num>月</measure>
<num value="47">庚戌</num>
<pc>，</pc>晉<placeName>易州</placeName>戍將孫方簡請內附<pc>。</pc>
